00:40:31,012 --> 00:40:33,473
There's a super popular
macaron place nearby.

455
00:40:33,557 --> 00:40:34,558
Finish up, let's go.

456
00:40:34,850 --> 00:40:36,935
Slow down. We got time.

457
00:40:37,227 --> 00:40:39,187
