612
00:54:12,792 --> 00:54:16,545
It's better to go outside.
Get some fresh air, you know?

613
00:54:17,046 --> 00:54:20,841
"Even a broken clock is right
twice a day." You're right about that.

614
00:54:21,092 --> 00:54:23,260
